videos.description: Iowa State's Cameron Lard gets the ball in the paint and lays it in with his back to the net.
videos.headline: Lard sinks shot from tough angle

videos.description: Cameron Lard shows no mercy on the rim by flying through the paint for the dunk.
videos.headline: Lard throws down huge contested slam

videos.description: Kansas' Lagerald Vick lobs it to Udoka Azubuike for the two-handed throw down.
videos.headline: Vick finds Azubuike for the jam

videos.description: Iowa State's Lindell Wigginton misses the three and Solomon Young is strong off the boards to one-hand jam the rebound.
videos.headline: Young  slams home the rebound

videos.description: Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk drives and dishes to Udoka Azubuike for the two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Azubuike continues to punish the rim

videos.description: Lagerald Vick lobs it to Udoka Azubuike for another alley-oop.
videos.headline: Azubuike cannot be stopped

videos.description: Iowa State moves the ball all over the floor and Zoran Talley Jr. finally drives through the paint for the lay-in.
videos.headline: Iowa State's huge ball movement leads to points

videos.description: Zoran Talley Jr. muscles through the paint for the bucket and draws the foul for the potential 3-point play.
videos.headline: Talley drives for crucial and-1
